# Project Intelligence (.cursorrules)

## Patterns
- Use `AppRoutes` for navigation and centralized route definitions.
- Keep API base URL logic in `ApiConfig`; avoid scattering base URLs.
- Prefer `provider` for shared state; use `shared_preferences` only for simple persistence.

## Preferences
- Consistent theming via `ThemeData` and seed color; font `Roboto`.
- Use fade transitions for service/dashboard navigations.

## Workflows
- When adding features, create `state/`, `models/`, `widgets/` subfolders per module.
- Document any new endpoints and request/response models in Memory Bank.

